    <item>
      <title>特朗普临近提名，加强对共和党的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/trump-tightens-grasp-on-republican-party-as-he-nears-nomination</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普正在采取行动巩固对共和党的权力，这预示着他在可能的第二个任期内要求的忠诚度，因为他正处于赢得共和党总统提名的风口浪尖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/trump-tightens-grasp-on-republican-party-as-he-nears-nomination</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 18:10:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
